      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age. The engine and transmission are functional, but you may notice some minor fluid leaks and a bit of hesitation during cold starts. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and some paint fading, while the interior shows significant wear on the upholstery and a few non-essential electronic quirks. It is a solid choice for someone looking for a budget-friendly option who doesn't mind performing some upcoming maintenance and cosmetic touch-ups.",
